window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A sickness runs rampant through the world. In Portland, Oregon it is no different. As the night takes hold, eight men and women bear witness to the horror of a zombie outbreak. <i>This Rotten World</i> is the zombie novel that horror fans have been waiting for. Where other zombie works skip over the best part of a zombie outbreak, <i>This Rotten World</i> revels in it the downfall of humanity, dragging you through the beginnings of society's death, kicking and screaming.</p>"; 
